org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.tigr.contig

Interface TigrContigFileVisitor


  • public interface TigrContigFileVisitor
    TigrContigFileVisitor is a visitor interface to visit contigs of a TIGR .contig encoded file.
    Author:
    dkatzel

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static interface  TigrContigFileVisitor.TigrContigVisitorCallback
      TigrContigVisitorCallback is a callback mechanism to allow the TigrContigVisitor instances to communicate with the parser that is parsing the contig file.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void halted()
      The parser has stopped parsing but has not actually finished the parsing the file, this will happen only if a visitor calls TigrContigFileVisitor.TigrContigVisitorCallback.haltParsing().
      TigrContigVisitor visitContig(TigrContigFileVisitor.TigrContigVisitorCallback callback, String contigId)
      A new Contig has been detected in the contig file.
      void visitEnd()
      The entire file was visited.

    • Method Detail

      • visitContig

        TigrContigVisitor visitContig(TigrContigFileVisitor.TigrContigVisitorCallback callback,
                              String contigId)
        A new Contig has been detected in the contig file.
        Parameters:
        callback - an instance of TigrContigFileVisitor.TigrContigVisitorCallback; will never be null.
        contigId - the contig id of this contig.
        Returns:
        a TigrContigVisitor instance if this contig should be visited; if null is returned, then this contig will not be visited.

      • halted

        void halted()
        The parser has stopped parsing but has not actually finished the parsing the file, this will happen only if a visitor calls TigrContigFileVisitor.TigrContigVisitorCallback.haltParsing().

      • visitEnd

        void visitEnd()
        The entire file was visited.
